      <title>有报道称特朗普可能削减关税计划，铜价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华盛顿邮报》报道称，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的助手正在研究适用于所有国家但仅涵盖主要商品进口的关税计划，此后伦敦铜价上涨逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/metals-steady-as-china-shows-support-for-under-pressure-currency</guid>
